data.description: Sellers have a 4.125% assumable VA loan, call for details. Nestled on a sprawling 2-acre parcel, this home offers an idyllic retreat for those seeking a perfect homestead. This charming property has undergone recent upgrades, including brand new insulation and roof installations for both the house and the outbuilding, ensuring modern comfort and protection (completed in 2023). The newly added gutters (2023) contribute to the property's impeccable maintenance standards. Freshly painted interiors (2023) provide a crisp and inviting ambiance, while the HVAC system, installed in 2017, guarantees year-round climate control. Prospective buyers will appreciate the waterproof basement liner, professionally installed in 2019, with a transferable warranty. The contemporary kitchen boasts a stunning redesign, and the bathrooms were tastefully updated in 2019, creating a harmonious blend of functionality and elegance.
